ion a 5-star rating. The boathouse is at the front of our river house. It’s a deep waterfront timber cabin with a cosy sleeping loft. Perfect for couples. Pitched ceilings and roaring fires. Bushwalking, picnics, reading and snoozing. Only an hour by car from the harbour bridge. Or on the train from Central. And a five minute boat ride from Brooklyn. 100% of recent guests gave the location a 5-star rating. 12 recent guests said this place was sparkling clean. Relax in the beautiful warmth of a unique strawbale cottage after spending the day enjoying the stunning natural beauty of the Blue Mountains. Situated in Leura but backing onto bushland, you''ll adore the cosy atmosphere and comforts in this home away from home. Wi-Fi Take in serene views of Pittwater and the Pacific Ocean from both the inside and outside of this delightful studio cottage. Set in a quiet natural environment, there are modern amenities for two people, plus complete privacy.');
